Direct Known Subclasses:
CommonDialog
public class MxFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.awt.event.WindowListener, DragAndDropFrame

This class represent a matrix dialog. Our dialogs can have menus and toolbars. The AWT Dialog class does not support menus that is why we extended Frame. This class also traps mouse events and pops up a tooltip window.
